Class CachingMap.PrimingListener

java.lang.Object
com.tangosol.util.Base
com.tangosol.util.MultiplexingMapListener
com.tangosol.net.cache.CachingMap.PrimingListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
MapListener, MapListenerSupport.PrimingListener, MapListenerSupport.SynchronousListener, SynchronousListener, EventListener
Enclosing class:
CachingMap<K,V>
protected class CachingMap.PrimingListener extends MultiplexingMapListener implements MapListenerSupport.PrimingListener
MapListener for back map responsible for keeping the front map coherent with the back map. This listener is registered as a synchronous listener for lite events (carrying only a key) and generates a "priming" event when registered.
